---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Cohort">
  <h1>Cohort</h1>
  <p class="label">Our current research instrument</p>

  <div class="prose">
    <p>
      Cohort is an app we're building to test our
      hypothesis: Do others also studying around you improve focus among high
      school students without competition, leaderboards, points, or any other type of
      gamification?
    </p>
    <p>
      The app is small on purpose. A student creates or joins a session with
      3 to 6 friends, each participant can see who else is present and whether
      they are currently marked as focusing, and the only information shared is who is here and whether they are working.
    </p>
    <p>
      This simpler app is for research purposes, not for the product.
      If we added competition, we could not know whether
      focus improvement came from other's presence or from gamification.
    </p>

    <div class="panel">
      <p class="panel__label">Current status</p>
      <p class="panel__body">
        Cohort is in development. We plan to run structured testing sessions with
        volunteer students during the exam period in October and November 2026.
        We will report results in the devlog.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="links">
      <span class="muted">GitHub: coming soon</span>
      <span class="muted">Live version: not yet available</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }
</style>
